ActNational Defence Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Queen's Regulations and Orders for the Canadian Forces
PrecisRegulations Amending the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES in order to bring the Regulations into line with changes made to the National Defence Act. These regulatory amendments will enhance the military justice system in myriad ways.
